<br>
As to your usable drop idea its kinda already in effect but its called NODROP. Since if a item is NODROP only people that will use it have a reason to kill for it. Due to this fact we often invite a few people from smaller guilds along when we clear Fear to have any armor that would otherwise rot. NODROP also discourages the farming of items.  When EQ first came out it was only attached to some quest items if at all. They later made these changes making most items Lore and NODROP to prevent the farming of items. <p>Wyrmwood B'Dynn 60 Grave Lord <BR>

